PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1779181629
OL,3,CStars show off their gnomes as Chelsea
OL,4,CFlower Show gets under way
OL,6,FAnd ` with the RHS lifting its Chelsea
OL,7,Fgnome ban for only the second time in
OL,8,Fthe show's history ` visitors to the
OL,9,Fevent can spot one or two of the
OL,10,Fcheery ornaments in displays such as
OL,11,Fthe RHS and King's Foundation Curious
OL,12,FGarden, which aims to get people
OL,13,Fcurious about gardening.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/10
