CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1779181629
OL,3,CStars show off their gnomes as Chelsea
OL,4,CFlower Show gets under way
OL,6,FQueen guitarist Sir Brian May,
OL,7,Fcomedian Bill Bailey, TV gardener Alan
OL,8,FTitchmarsh and presenter Dame Floella
OL,9,FBenjamin were among those who were
OL,10,Fshowing off their gnomes ` which are
OL,11,Fbeing auctioned for the RHS's Campaign
OL,12,Ffor School Gardening to help children
OL,13,Faccess gardening
OL,15,FBailey said gnomes have been "much
OL,16,Fmaligned".
OL,18,F"The Romans had them as guardians of
OL,19,Fthe dark, and to protect against
OL,20,Fmalign spirits," he said.
OL,26,@wD@^OUxD@IO]zD@AOU|D@PO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/10
