PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1779181629
OL,3,CStars show off their gnomes as Chelsea
OL,4,CFlower Show gets under way
OL,6,FAsked if it took him a long time to
OL,7,Fdecorate his gnome, comedian Tom Allen
OL,8,Fsaid: "Oh, ages."
OL,10,F"Mine's got a suit and tie on, which I
OL,11,Fdon't think they normally wear. He
OL,12,Fdoesn't have any eyes. So, it's about
OL,13,Fa dozing thing."
OL,15,FTitchmarsh, who was wearing a blue
OL,16,Fsuit, said: "I did mine to match me."
OL,18,FAsked if Chelsea had taken itself too
OL,19,Fseriously with its themes in recent
OL,20,Fyears, Titchmarsh said: "It doesn't
OL,21,Ftake itself seriously.
OL,26,@pD@GOUpD@QO]rD@AOUuD@PO]xD@MOUxD@eO]|D@
OL,26,AYOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/10
