OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1779181629
OL,3,CStars show off their gnomes as Chelsea
OL,4,CFlower Show gets under way
OL,6,F"It takes gardening seriously, which
OL,7,Fmore people should do ` seriously, in
OL,8,Fthat it's important, but it's all
OL,9,Fabout fun and improving everybody's
OL,10,Fwellbeing, being out in the garden,
OL,11,Fyou feel better."
OL,13,FTitchmarsh said "misery" would be the
OL,14,Fone thing he banned from the Chelsea
OL,15,FFlower Show, while Allen said: "I'd be
OL,16,Finclined to ban leaf blowers."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@QO]uD@QOUuD@XO]wD@`OUxD@^O]
