CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1779181629
OL,3,CStars show off their gnomes as Chelsea
OL,4,CFlower Show gets under way
OL,6,FClare Matterson, director general of
OL,7,Fthe RHS, said she was thrilled with
OL,8,Fthe King's Foundation Curious Garden,
OL,9,Fa centrepiece at Chelsea that aims to
OL,10,Fencourage people to get curious about
OL,11,Fgardening and which has been designed
OL,12,Fwith input from the King, Sir David
OL,13,FBeckham and Titchmarsh.
OL,15,FSpeaking about the gnome auction, Ms
OL,16,FMatterson said: "Every penny will go
OL,17,Fto support the RHS Campaign for School
OL,18,FGardening so we can get children up
OL,19,Fand down this country enjoying the
OL,20,Fbenefits, the joy, the health, the
OL,21,Flearning of gardening."
OL,26,@xD@QOU}D@WO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/10
