OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1779181629
OL,3,CStars show off their gnomes as Chelsea
OL,4,CFlower Show gets under way
OL,6,FSir Brian's gnome, "Billy Bad-Axe",
OL,7,Fwhich comes complete with a guitar,
OL,8,Fhad already earned a bid of #650 by
OL,9,FMonday morning, with the auction
OL,10,Frunning until Sunday May 24.
OL,12,FThis year's Chelsea show features
OL,13,Fgardens including one championing
OL,14,F"edgelands" on urban fringes that
OL,15,Fconnect people with nature, from the
OL,16,FCampaign to Protect Rural England and
OL,17,Fdesigned by Sarah Eberle.
OL,26,@nD@TOUnD@bO]vD@AOUvD@KO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/10
