PN,40408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1779181629
OL,3,CStars show off their gnomes as Chelsea
OL,4,CFlower Show gets under way
OL,6,FThe garden centres on a huge piece of
OL,7,Fart, a Gaia ` Mother Nature ` figure,
OL,8,Flying across the garden, carved from a
OL,9,Ffallen mature tree and willow hair
OL,10,Fforming the top of a dry stone wall
OL,11,Fsnaking through the display of native
OL,12,Fand naturalised plants and flowers.
OL,14,FAlso among the show gardens is one
OL,15,Ffrom Tate Britain, inspired by the
OL,16,Fgallery's art ` and complete with a
OL,17,FBarbara Hepworth sculpture ` and which
OL,18,Fwill be moved to Tate Britain's
OL,19,FMillbank site after Chelsea.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
